>i am thinking of buying a hall effect magnetic sensor. what is the model
>compatible with the HB and what is its sensing range.

Knudsen in his book (p 223) uses Digi-Key part number DN6847SE-ND, which, he
says, is "sticky" in the sense that it remains set until explicitly reset.  I
have no experience with it.

